### 5. Algorithm AS 63 - Incomplete Beta Function

**Location**: `src/fortran/external/as63.f90`
**Authors**: K.L. Majumder and G.P. Bhattacharjee
**Reference**: Applied Statistics (1973), Volume 22, Number 3, pages 409-411
**Copyright**: Royal Statistical Society
**License**: Freely redistributable with no fee charged

The Royal Statistical Society holds the copyright to this routine and has given
permission for its distribution provided that no fee is charged.

