**License**: Public Domain
**Source**: http://www.johndcook.com/julia_rng.html

The original code is explicitly placed in the public domain with no restrictions.

---

## BLAS and LAPACK

This software uses BLAS and LAPACK libraries for linear algebra operations. These
libraries are typically provided by the user's system and are not bundled with
this software. BLAS and LAPACK reference implementations are in the public domain.

